The paper focuses on optimizing the execution efficiency of neural personalized recommendation, which is a key component of many cloud services and products. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the design and deployment of a system for recommendation use cases, which suggests that it may also belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
